description: Returns information on a specific signing profile.

parameters.name: profileName
parameters.description: The name of the target signing profile.

nested_items.name: profileName
nested_items.description: The name of the target signing profile.

nested_items.name: profileVersion
nested_items.description: The current version of the signing profile.

nested_items.name: profileVersionArn
nested_items.description: The signing profile ARN, including the profile version.

nested_items.name: revocationRecord
nested_items.description: Revocation information for a signing profile.

nested_items.name: revocationEffectiveFrom
nested_items.description: The time when revocation becomes effective.

nested_items.name: revokedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the signing profile was revoked.

nested_items.name: revokedBy
nested_items.description: The identity of the revoker.

nested_items.name: signingMaterial
nested_items.description: The ARN of the certificate that the target profile uses for signing operations.

nested_items.name: certificateArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the certificates that is used to sign your code.

nested_items.name: platformId
nested_items.description: The ID of the platform that is used by the target signing profile.

nested_items.name: platformDisplayName
nested_items.description: A human-readable name for the signing platform associated with the signing profile.

nested_items.name: signatureValidityPeriod
nested_items.description: The validity period for a signing job.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The numerical value of the time unit for signature validity.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The time unit for signature validity.

nested_items.name: overrides
nested_items.description: A list of overrides applied by the target signing profile for signing operations.

nested_items.name: signingConfiguration
nested_items.description: A signing configuration that overrides the default encryption or hash algorithm of a signing job.

nested_items.name: encryptionAlgorithm
nested_items.description: A specified override of the default encryption algorithm that is used in a code-signing job.

nested_items.name: hashAlgorithm
nested_items.description: A specified override of the default hash algorithm that is used in a code-signing job.

nested_items.name: signingImageFormat
nested_items.description: A signed image is a JSON object. When overriding the default signing platform configuration, a customer can select either of two signing formats, JSONEmbedded or JSONDetached. (A third format value, JSON, is reserved for future use.) With JSONEmbedded, the signing image has the payload embedded in it. With JSONDetached, the payload is not be embedded in the signing image.

nested_items.name: signingParameters
nested_items.description: A map of key-value pairs for signing operations that is attached to the target signing profile.
(string) ---
(string) ---

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the target signing profile.

nested_items.name: statusReason
nested_items.description: Reason for the status of the target signing profile.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the signing profile.
